Package model

Describes all the Adrenaline game objects and parts
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Match
    This is the most important class of model package Contains all the match information, from the players, to the map, the decks and the killshotTrack
    ShootingParametersInput
    this class is a container of fields that will be setted by the user during the shooting action
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Color
    This enum gives all the possible colors in the game it's largely used across a lot of classes
    ShootMode
    This enumeration contains the list of all the possible shooting modes of all the weapons in the game
